            </div>
            <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-4">Source-Available</h2>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-400 mb-8 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-pretty">
                Our entire codebase is available on GitHub with a source-available license. Anyone can view and contribute.
            </p>
            <button class="bg-white text-dark-bg px-8 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-gray-100 transition-all shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105">
                Contribute
